metadata.name: Bricked
metadata.description:
|Coin-Laundry Open Editions| 
Big News at Coin-Laundry! The shop next to the Laundromat was for sale, we'd been eyeing it up for years... i think that old lady finally kicked the bucket...Long story short; 

INTRODUCING:  
FINE ART DEPOT | Monthly Open Editions | By: Coin-Laundry

First week of each month - 1 Open Edition will be created  
-each piece will be hand made digital and/or physical work 

OPEN EDITION PERKS:  
-Unreleased Coin-Laundry works, pieces that don't quite fit in the OG collection, or hyper topical conversations  
-Personal Print Rights  
-A drawing for a 1/1 every 25 OEs sold  
-Burn to Earn  
-At the end of each month ALL OE TOKENS ARE ENTERED INTO A DRAWING FOR A PHYSICAL PIECE
